Windows Build
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Build with Visual Studio 2017 with Release/x64 configuration. Then run 
test.bat from the command line.

Linux Build
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Build with gradle. It will detect and use gcc or clang compiler. Make
sure the active compiler version supports C++11 (eg gcc 7). Then run
test.sh. To build:
./gradlew assembleRelease

